cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object recognition and semantic segmentation tasks using deep learning models. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions the transformation of instance segmentation masks into 3D bounding boxes, which could be useful for robotics applications. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses deep learning models for object recognition. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as the paper uses deep learning models for object recognition and semantic segmentation. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with 360 panoramic images and their integration into 3D models of rooms.
